query:
PREFIX rdf:type: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type<
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri ?string 
WHERE {
   ?uri rdf:type <http://purl.org/ontology/mo/Record> . 
   ?uri dc:title ?string .
   ?album owl:sameAs ?uri .
   ?album <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/releaseDate> ?date . 
   <http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_F._Kennedy> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/birthDate> ?start .
   <http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_F._Kennedy> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/deathDate> ?end .
   FILTER (?date >= ?start && ?date <=> ?end)
}

query:
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri ?string
WHERE {
  ?label <http://dbpedia.org/property/parent> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sony_Music_Entertainment> .
  ?dbp_band <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/recordLabel> ?label .
  ?dbp_band owl:sameAs ?mb_band .
  ?uri rdf:type <http://purl.org/ontology/mo/Record> .
  ?uri <http://purl.org/ontology/mo/release_type> <http://purl.org/ontology/mo/single> .
  ?uri <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/maker> ?mb_band .
  ?uri dc:title ?string .
}

query:
SELECT DISTINCT
WHERE {
  ?album rdf:type <http://purl.org/ontology/mo/Record> .
  ?album <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/title> 'Drunken Lullabies' .
  ?album <http://purl.org/ontology/mo/singer> ?mb_singer .
  ?album <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/maker> ?mb_band .
  ?mb_band <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/name> 'Flogging Molly' .
  ?dbp_singer owl:sameAs ?mb_singer .
  ?dbp_singer <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/birthPlace> ?city .
  ?city <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/country> ?uri .
  ?uri rdf:type <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Country> .
}
question: In which country was the singer of the Drunken Lullabies by Flogging Molly born?

query:
SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?uri) as ?count)
WHERE {
  ?dbp_band rdf:type <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Band> .
  ?dbp_band <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/recordLabel> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roadrunner_Records> .
  ?dbp_band owl:sameAs ?mb_band .
  ?uri rdf:type <http://purl.org/ontology/mo/Record> .
  ?uri <http://purl.org/ontology/mo/release_type> <http://purl.org/ontology/mo/single> .
  ?uri <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/maker> ?mb_band .
}
question: How many singles were produced by bands under contract with Roadrunner Records.

query:
ASK
WHERE {
  ?mb_band <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/name> 'The Cracow Klezmer Band' .
  ?mb_band <http://purl.org/vocab/bio/0.1/event> ?event .
  ?event rdf:type <http://purl.org/vocab/bio/0.1/Birth> .
  ?event <http://purl.org/vocab/bio/0.1/date> ?birthdate1 . 
  <http://dbpedia.org/resource/DJ_Tomekk> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/birthDate> ?birthdate2 .
  FILTER (?birthdate1 <=> ?birthdate2)
}
